text: Kenny Stephenson (born 12 June 1938) is a British wrestler. He competed at the 1960 Summer Olympics and the 1964 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1938 births Category:Living people Category:British male sport wrestlers Category:Olympic wrestlers of Great Britain Category:Wrestlers at the 1960 Summer Olympics Category:Wrestlers at the 1964 Summer Olympics Category:Sportspeople from Bury, Greater Manchester
